  <brief_title>Study Investigating the Best Method of Treatment of Bile Duct Stones in Higher Risk Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomised Clinical Trial to Compare Endoscopic Sphincterotomy and Subsequent Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy With Primary Laparoscopic Bile Duct Exploration During Cholecystectomy in Higher Risk Patients With Choledocholithiasis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
